  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Dungeon-Doku, a rogue-lite twist on the classic Sudoku puzzle game, with monsters, traps and treasures galore.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Unlimited Puzzles</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every delve into the dungeon is different with procedural generated Sudoku puzzles with 4 levels of difficulty and randomly spawning traps to add spice.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Traps Change Traditional Game Play</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to collect as many useful things as possible in the first stages because when you hit the traps, it will get a bit more difficult.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236110/extras/d435a30c3fcfc2d49a7514acb918768a.avif?t=1773943274\" width=455 height=345 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Over 30 Treasures</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Besides multiple levels of armor to keep you safe, there are antidotes to treat your poison, keys to open locks, health positions to heal you from a misstep and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236110/extras/7ef78ffda1b7a23e8f97345d8173878d.avif?t=1773943274\" alt=\"\"width=256 height=313 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Dungeon-Doku, a rogue-lite twist on the classic Sudoku puzzle game, with monsters, traps and treasures galore.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Unlimited Puzzles</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every delve into the dungeon is different with procedural generated Sudoku puzzles with 4 levels of difficulty and randomly spawning traps to add spice.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Traps Change Traditional Game Play</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make sure to collect as many useful things as possible in the first stages because when you hit the traps, it will get a bit more difficult.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236110/extras/d435a30c3fcfc2d49a7514acb918768a.avif?t=1773943274\" width=455 height=345 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><strong>Over 30 Treasures</strong></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Besides multiple levels of armor to keep you safe, there are antidotes to treat your poison, keys to open locks, health positions to heal you from a misstep and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4236110/extras/7ef78ffda1b7a23e8f97345d8173878d.avif?t=1773943274\" alt=\"\"width=256 height=313 /></span></p>",
